item.dc:creator: @pko pko
item.description:
@pko wrote:

Go to www.no-ip.com

Register with your email.

Login

Press “Hosts/Redirects”

Go to the “Add” tab

Put in your Host name (server name), then press “create host”

run your you server, and then people can get on via your hostname
